========================Pre-requisites====================

1. ruby -v 1.9.3p194

2. rspec -v 2.12.0 (Please perform gem install rspec..incase machine do not have rspec)

===================To run the test cases===================

1. Go to the particular directory path
2. run command rspec

===================To run the program===================

1. Go to the particular directory path
2. run commands individually    			
	1.ruby billing_system_utility.rb customer

	2.ruby billing_system_utility.rb customer 12/12/2009

	3.ruby billing_system_utility.rb employee

	4.ruby billing_system_utility.rb affiliate			  

